    "originContent": "If you have [rust](https://www.rust-lang.org) setup use the following command:",
    "translatedContent": "[rust](https://www.rust-lang.org)이 설정되어 있다면 다음 명령어를 사용하세요:"
  },
  {
    "row": 11,
    "rowsha": "8bkBhHOQsO1+N058HkZOwXtGpCfEh6WtbL0pBkBQg9U=",
    "originContent": "```",
    "translatedContent": "```"
  },
  {
    "row": 12,
    "rowsha": "aWEnRfMneQAIfLDJNncqGCqrAQ/B3b3Jl/AlResnN+k=",
    "originContent": "cargo install typst-live",
    "translatedContent": "cargo install typst-live"
  },
  {
    "row": 13,
    "rowsha": "8bkBhHOQsO1+N058HkZOwXtGpCfEh6WtbL0pBkBQg9U=",
    "originContent": "```",
